room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Chattanooga in Chattanooga
review: We did the kidnapping game on our trip. The game was challenging, intriguing, and very well put together. It is well worth the price. Not very expensive, and makes for a much more fun night than going to the movies. Highly recommended.
